msgctxt "3872_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Kiryu-san!?"
msgstr "¡¿Kiryu-san?!"

msgctxt "3884_Player"
msgid "Sorry to keep you waiting."
msgstr "Lamento hacerle esperar."

msgctxt "3896_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Umm... Wasn't it supposed to be just us two?"
msgstr "Umm... Wasn't it supposed to be just us two?"

msgctxt "3908_Talk_No"
msgid "This isn't date-like at all..."
msgstr "This isn't date-like at all..."

msgctxt "3920_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "3932_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I'll be waiting here, so come back on your own, okay?"
msgstr "I'll be waiting here, so come back on your own, okay?"

msgctxt "3944_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hey! You're late! What, did you just forget about me!?"
msgstr "Hey! You're late! What, did you just forget about me!?"

msgctxt "3956_Player"
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr "Lo siento..."

msgctxt "3968_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Well, okay. But you'd better make it up to me."
msgstr "Well, okay. But you'd better make it up to me."

msgctxt "3980_Player"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Está bien."

msgctxt "4040_Yasu"
msgid "Well, well, look who it is. Kyoko, from my new favorite band, The Orpheus."
msgstr "Bueno, bueno, Miren a quien tenemos aquí. Kyoko, de mi banda favorita, The Orpheus."

msgctxt "4052_Yasu"
msgid "Whoa. You're not on a date, are you?"
msgstr "Vaya. No están en una cita, ¿no?"

msgctxt "4064_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "That's none of your business! Get lost!"
msgstr "¡Esto no te incumbe! ¡Piérdete!"

msgctxt "4076_Yasu"
msgid "Charming as always."
msgstr "Encantadora como siempre."

msgctxt "4088_Player"
msgid "Who are these guys?"
msgstr "¿Quiénes a estos tipos?"

msgctxt "4100_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Don't worry about them."
msgstr "No te preocupes por ellos."

msgctxt "4112_Yasu"
msgid "Wait, you work at a hostess club too, right? So this is a customer! Lucky you, he looks like quite a catch."
msgstr "Espera, trabajas en un club de hostess también, ¿no? ¡Y él es un cliente! Qué suerte tienes, ¡Es un tipazo!"

msgctxt "4124_Yasu"
msgid "And your band's getting sooo popular now, too."
msgstr "Y tu banda está siendo muuuy popular ahora también."

msgctxt "4136_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "You better cut it out or I'm gonna lose it!"
msgstr "¡Será mejor que pares o voy a perder la paciencia!"

msgctxt "4148_Yasu"
msgid "I just hope your success doesn't affect your \"music.\" Haha!"
msgstr "Espero que tu éxito no afecte tu \"musica\". ¡Jajaja!"

msgctxt "4196_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "4208_Player"
msgid "What's the deal with them?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es el trato con ellos?"

msgctxt "4220_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "They're from a band called Bad Flag. They're infamous for being pretty aggressive."
msgstr "Ellos son de una banda llamada Bad Flag. Son famosos por ser muy agresivos."

msgctxt "4232_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I heard they target popular bands and try to take them down a notch or two."
msgstr "Escuché que van por bandas populares e intentan bajarlas de una u otra forma."

msgctxt "4244_Player"
msgid "Is that so?"
msgstr "Con que así son las cosas."

msgctxt "4256_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Sorry about all of this. I didn't mean to ruin our date."
msgstr "Siento lo que paso. No quería arruinar nuestra cita."

msgctxt "4268_Player"
msgid "Of course not."
msgstr "Claro que no."

msgctxt "4280_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Anyway, where do you want to go?"
msgstr "De todos modos, ¿Dónde quieres ir?"

msgctxt "4304_Player"
msgid "(Where should we go...)"
msgstr "(¿A qué lugar deberíamos ir...?)"

msgctxt "4316_Player"
msgid "(Where should we go...)"
msgstr "(¿A qué lugar deberíamos ir...?)"

msgctxt "4328_Player"
msgid "(We could go shopping.)"
msgstr "(¿A dónde deberíamos ir de compras...?)"

msgctxt "4340_Player"
msgid "(We could go out to eat.)"
msgstr "(¿A dónde deberíamos ir a comer...?)"

msgctxt "4352_Player"
msgid "(What should we do?)"
msgstr "(¿Qué deberíamos hacer...?)"

msgctxt "4376_Player"
msgid "How about Kanrai for some yakiniku?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece si vamos a Kanrai por un poco de yakiniku?"

msgctxt "4388_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Yakiniku? Now that I think of it, I am kinda hungry."
msgstr "Yakiniku? Now that I think of it, I am kinda hungry."

msgctxt "4400_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Anyway, you wanna get going?"
msgstr "Anyway, you wanna get going?"

msgctxt "4424_Player"
msgid "How about Kanrai for some yakiniku?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece si vamos a Kanrai por un poco de yakiniku?"

msgctxt "4436_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Yakiniku again? You sure like that stuff, huh?"
msgstr "Yakiniku again? You sure like that stuff, huh?"

msgctxt "4448_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "You just want to go there for yourself, right? Can't you ever think about what I want to eat?"
msgstr "You just want to go there for yourself, right? Can't you ever think about what I want to eat?"

msgctxt "4460_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Whatever. Anyway, you wanna get going?"
msgstr "Whatever. Anyway, you wanna get going?"

msgctxt "4496_Player"
msgid "How does Sushi Gin sound?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece ir al Sushi Gin?"

msgctxt "4508_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Sushi? Heheh... It just so happens that I love sushi. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default> Now that I think of it, I am kinda hungry."
msgstr "Sushi? Heheh... It just so happens that I love sushi. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default> Now that I think of it, I am kinda hungry."

msgctxt "4520_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Anyway, you wanna get going?"
msgstr "Anyway, you wanna get going?"

msgctxt "4544_Player"
msgid "How does Sushi Gin sound?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece ir al Sushi Gin?"

msgctxt "4556_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Sushi again? You sure like that stuff, huh?"
msgstr "Sushi again? You sure like that stuff, huh?"

msgctxt "4568_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "You just want to go there for yourself, right? Can't you ever think about what I want to eat?"
msgstr "You just want to go there for yourself, right? Can't you ever think about what I want to eat?"

msgctxt "4580_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Whatever. Anyway, you wanna get going?"
msgstr "Whatever. Anyway, you wanna get going?"

msgctxt "4616_Player"
msgid "Why don't we go shopping at Le Marche?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece si vamos de compras a Le Marche?"

msgctxt "4628_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh my gosh... You're going to buy me something?"
msgstr "Oh my gosh... You're going to buy me something?"

msgctxt "4640_Talk_Angry"
msgid "Seriously!? I'd be super happy to get a present from you, Kiryu-san! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Seriously!? I'd be super happy to get a present from you, Kiryu-san! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4652_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Alright, then let's get on over there! ♪"
msgstr "¡Muy bien, vamos!"

msgctxt "4676_Player"
msgid "Why don't we go shopping at Le Marche?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece si vamos de compras a Le Marche?"

msgctxt "4688_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oooh. Are you gonna buy me something again!? I feel kinda bad. That wasn't the reason I came on a date with you."
msgstr "Oooh. Are you gonna buy me something again!? I feel kinda bad. That wasn't the reason I came on a date with you."

msgctxt "4700_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Whatever. Anyway, you wanna get going?"
msgstr "Whatever. Anyway, you wanna get going?"

msgctxt "4736_Player"
msgid "Why don't we try something different and get a bite at Watami?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no hacemos algo diferente y comemos algo en Watami?"

msgctxt "4748_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hey, that's not a bad idea! ♪ We come to Watami a lot for after parties for our band. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Ey, no es mala idea! ♪ Vamos a muchas veces a Watami después de las fiestas de la banda. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4760_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Awesome. Then let's head on over."
msgstr "Awesome. Then let's head on over."

msgctxt "4784_Player"
msgid "Why don't we try something different and get a bite at Watami?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no hacemos algo diferente y comemos algo en Watami?"

msgctxt "4796_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Okay! That's kinda your go-to date location, huh, Kiryu-san? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Okay! That's kinda your go-to date location, huh, Kiryu-san? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4808_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Anyway, you wanna get going?"
msgstr "Anyway, you wanna get going?"

msgctxt "4844_Player"
msgid "Should we go bowling?"
msgstr "¿Vamos a los bolos?"

msgctxt "4856_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Bowling, huh? I haven't been playing much lately, so I wonder if I'll be any good."
msgstr "Bowling, huh? I haven't been playing much lately, so I wonder if I'll be any good."

msgctxt "4868_Talk_Smile"
msgid "It's on, Kiryu-san. ♪"
msgstr "It's on, Kiryu-san. ♪"

msgctxt "4880_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Let's head on over."
msgstr "Let's head on over."

msgctxt "4904_Player"
msgid "Should we go bowling?"
msgstr "¿Vamos a los bolos?"

msgctxt "4916_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Again? You sure like bowling, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "Again? You sure like bowling, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "4928_Talk_Smile"
msgid "If we're going on a date, I'd rather we go somewhere different than last time..."
msgstr "If we're going on a date, I'd rather we go somewhere different than last time..."

msgctxt "4940_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Well, whatever. Let's head on over then."
msgstr "Well, whatever. Let's head on over then."

msgctxt "4976_Player"
msgid "Should we go play darts at Bantam?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal si jugamos a los dardos en Bantam?"

msgctxt "4988_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Ooh, darts! ♪ It's perfect for someone as cool as me. ♪"
msgstr "Ooh, darts! ♪ It's perfect for someone as cool as me. ♪"

msgctxt "5000_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Awesome. Then let's head on over."
msgstr "Awesome. Then let's head on over."

msgctxt "5024_Player"
msgid "Should we go play darts at Bantam?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal si jugamos a los dardos en Bantam?"

msgctxt "5036_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Darts again? Mm, sorry, but couldn't we go somewhere different this time?"
msgstr "Darts again? Mm, sorry, but couldn't we go somewhere different this time?"

msgctxt "5060_P_sitsofa_tlk_kamae"
msgid "Right, should we head out, then?"
msgstr "Right, should we head out, then?"

msgctxt "5096_Player"
msgid "Want to go sing karaoke?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal si vamos al karaoke?"

msgctxt "5108_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Ahaha! Okay, okay! You want to hear me sing for you, huh, Kiryu-san? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! ¡Bien me gusta! ¿Así que quieres que cante para ti? Eh, ¿Kiryu-san? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5120_Talk_Smile"
msgid "I'll sing my heart out for you, then!"
msgstr "¡Cantaré con todo mi corazón, solo para ti!"

msgctxt "5144_Player"
msgid "Want to go sing karaoke?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal si vamos al karaoke?"

msgctxt "5156_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hehehe... You're completely hooked on my singing voice, huh, Kiryu-san? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hehehe... You're completely hooked on my singing voice, huh, Kiryu-san? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5168_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Okay, let's head out!"
msgstr "Okay, let's head out!"

msgctxt "5204_Player"
msgid "Let's shoot some pool."
msgstr "¿Qué tal algo de billar?"

msgctxt "5216_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Pool? %s-san, you know how to play pool?"
msgstr "¿Billar? %s-san, ¿sabes cómo jugar al billar?"

msgctxt "5240_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Shall we get going?"
msgstr "¿Nos vamos?"

msgctxt "5264_Player"
msgid "Let's shoot some pool."
msgstr "¿Qué tal algo de billar?"

msgctxt "5276_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Pool again? If we're going on a date, I'd rather we go somewhere different than last time..."
msgstr "¿Otra vez billar? Si vamos a salir preferiría ir a un lugar diferente que mi último cita..."

msgctxt "5300_P_sitsofa_tlk_kamae"
msgid "Let's get going, then."
msgstr "Entonces, vamos."

msgctxt "5336_Player"
msgid "Let's play golf."
msgstr "¿Qué te parece jugar golf?"

msgctxt "5348_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Golf? Wow, Kiryu-san, you play golf?"
msgstr "Golf? Wow, Kiryu-san, you play golf?"

msgctxt "5360_P_sitsofa_tlk_kamae"
msgid "I've never played before, so you better teach me how to play!"
msgstr "I've never played before, so you better teach me how to play!"

msgctxt "5372_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Right, should we head out, then?"
msgstr "Right, should we head out, then?"

msgctxt "5396_Player"
msgid "Let's play golf."
msgstr "¿Qué te parece jugar golf?"

msgctxt "5408_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Golf again? We just did that the other day, and it takes so long. I'd rather do something we can get over and done with quick."
msgstr "Golf again? We just did that the other day, and it takes so long. I'd rather do something we can get over and done with quick."

msgctxt "5432_P_sitsofa_tlk_kamae"
msgid "Right, should we head out, then?"
msgstr "Right, should we head out, then?"

msgctxt "5468_Player"
msgid "Let's hit the hot springs."
msgstr "¿Vamos a las aguas termales?"

msgctxt "5480_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hot springs and table tennis? I'm pretty good at table tennis! I also sing in the bath! <Color:7>♥♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¿Aguas termales y una partida de ping-pong? Je, je. ¡Soy muy buena jugando! ¡También canto en el baño! <Color:7>♥♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5492_Talk_Smile"
msgid "Hehehe... What should I song today? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Je, je, je... Mmm, ¿qué debería cantar? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5504_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Shall we get going?"
msgstr "¿Nos vamos?"

msgctxt "5528_Player"
msgid "Let's play table tennis at the hot springs."
msgstr "Vayamos a jugar al ping-pong en las aguas termales."

msgctxt "5540_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Again? %s-san, you must really like table tennis."
msgstr "Again? %s-san, you must really like table tennis."

msgctxt "5552_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Heheheh. You can't beat me, Kiryu-san. Shall we get going?"
msgstr "Heheheh. You can't beat me, Kiryu-san. Shall we get going?"

msgctxt "5576_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san. You're here!"
msgstr "Oh, Kiryu-san. ¡Estás aquí!"

msgctxt "5588_Talk_Smile"
msgid "And just on time, too. That's so you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "And just on time, too. That's so you, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "5648_Yasu"
msgid "Well, well, look who it is. Kyoko, from my new favorite band, The Orpheus."
msgstr "Bueno, bueno, Miren a quien tenemos aquí. Kyoko, de mi banda favorita, The Orpheus."

msgctxt "5660_Yasu"
msgid "Whoa. You're not on a date, are you?"
msgstr "Vaya. No están en una cita, ¿no?"

msgctxt "5672_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "That's none of your business! Get lost!"
msgstr "¡Esto no te incumbe! ¡Piérdete!"

msgctxt "5684_Yasu"
msgid "Charming as always."
msgstr "Encantadora como siempre."

msgctxt "5696_Player"
msgid "Who are these guys?"
msgstr "¿Quiénes a estos tipos?"

msgctxt "5708_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Don't worry about them."
msgstr "No te preocupes por ellos."

msgctxt "5720_Yasu"
msgid "Wait, you work at a hostess club too, right? So this is a customer! Lucky you, he looks like quite a catch."
msgstr "Espera, trabajas en un club de hostess también, ¿no? ¡Y él es un cliente! Qué suerte tienes, ¡Es un tipazo!"

msgctxt "5732_Yasu"
